data.description: This exquisite custom-built home in the tranquil Saddle Creek community is set on a spacious .26-acre lot. Revel in the grandeur of high ceilings and elegant hand-scraped hardwood floors that lead you through a thoughtfully designed open floor plan. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek granite countertops, a grand island, and a walk-in pantry. The luxurious master suite is a haven of relaxation, offering a sitting area, jetted tub for unwinding, separate shower and dual vanities.. A versatile office space that can double as a bedroom, a large game room, and a dedicated media room for the ultimate entertainment experience. EnergyStarCertified, this home is equipped with modern green features, including solar panels and a backup generator to ensure comfort during power outages. The three-car garage provides ample storage, while the outdoor pool invites you to bask in the sun. Minutes from the Star, Mall, fine restaurants and short drive from both airports.
